OL,3,CMeasuring the scale of Starmer's
OL,4,Cwelfare reform debacle
OL,6,FHere is the scale of the government's
OL,7,Fhumiliation on Tuesday night.
OL,9,FA week ago, Downing St was warning any
OL,10,FLabour MP who was thinking of not
OL,11,Fvoting for the welfare reform that
OL,12,Fthey would never get a job on the
OL,13,Fpayroll.
OL,15,FAs late as Wednesday, the Treasury
OL,16,Finsisted there would be no backing
OL,17,Fdown.
