OL,3,CMeasuring the scale of Starmer's
OL,4,Cwelfare reform debacle
OL,6,FThe disability bill for government has
OL,7,Fbeen rising unsustainably fast.
OL,9,FMaybe some of that can be fixed as and
OL,10,Fwhen the NHS is fixed, or if an
OL,11,Feffective nationwide system of work
OL,12,Fcoaches is established.
OL,14,FBut is it remotely plausible that -
OL,15,Fafter the soon-to-be-established Timms
OL,16,Freview of eligibility criteria for
OL,17,Fdisability payments reports in 16 or
OL,18,F17 months - that the PM will risk
OL,19,Ftaking a penny away from any
OL,20,Fvulnerable person?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
