OL,3,CMeasuring the scale of Starmer's
OL,4,Cwelfare reform debacle
OL,6,FI can't find anyone close to him who
OL,7,Fthinks that kind of money-saving
OL,8,Fwelfare reform is still alive, in
OL,9,Fpractice.
OL,11,FThe true scale of this fiscal and
OL,12,Fpolitical catastrophe is that if the
OL,13,Fgovernment had reviewed the PIP and UC
OL,14,Fframework before announcing targets
OL,15,Ffor cuts, there might well have been
OL,16,Fscope to make serious savings.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
