OL,3,CMeasuring the scale of Starmer's
OL,4,Cwelfare reform debacle
OL,6,FBut in announcing that quantified
OL,7,Fsavings were the prime motivator, the
OL,8,FTreasury and Downing Street gave
OL,9,FLabour MPs an important cause, one
OL,10,Fthat trumps party loyalty - and they
OL,11,Fhave now closed down any prospect for
OL,12,FStarmer of curbing the growth of the
OL,13,Fwelfare budget for the foreseeable
OL,14,Ffuture.
